        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Today while farming in CC, I developed my new no-med solo strategy.</P><P>What I do is throw on a little bit of dex items to get my dex up. Then I equip a fast weapon (been using a velium dagger lately), and cast vampiric embrace. After the first round of combat, my pet has solid agro.. I mean, I can't taunt stuff off him to save my life. Then I sit there poking with my stupid dagger, healing myself on vampiric embrace procs. I keep allure of death up to keep mana coming.</P><P>Then as my pet starts to get worn down.. I pact him. And heal myself to full with vampiric embrace.</P><P>Sure it reduces me to shadowknight level, but it was kinda fun to run around meleeing for a while. ;)</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
